      "author": "nbDev99",
      "description": "Compliance release for the Obsidian Community Portal review.\r\n\r\n  **Fixes**\r\n  - Bump `minAppVersion` to 1.7.2 to match actual API usage (`Vault.createFolder`, `Workspace.revealLeaf`, `ButtonComponent.setDisabled`).\r\n\r\n  **Internal cleanup driven by review feedback**\r\n  - Replace all `createEl('div'|'span', ...)` sites with `createDiv` / `createSpan`.\r\n  - Switch `setTimeout` to `activeWindow.setTimeout` for popout-window compatibility.\r\n  - Type the parsed column-value JSON (status, people, date columns) to eliminate `any` warnings.\r\n  - Replace the deprecated `builtin-modules` package with Node's native `module.builtinModules`.\r\n  - Remove all `@ts-ignore` lines in favour of typed casts for Obsidian's internal settings API.\r\n\r\n  No user-facing behaviour changes.",
